• Integrity checks.
• Behavior changes when unauthorized modification or unpacking is detected.
Users may not interfere with these systems.

6. Termination
This license is automatically terminated if:
• The User violates any restriction.
• The User redistributes the Software without permission.
• The User modifies the Software without authorization.
Upon termination, the User must immediately cease all use of the Software.
The Copyright Holders may revoke permissions at any time.

